@startuml AI_DataExplorer_Sequence_Diagram

!theme cyborg
title AI Data Explorer — Sequence Diagram

skinparam backgroundColor #1a1a2e
skinparam defaultFontColor #e0e0e0
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam maxMessageSize 180

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #2d2d44
    BorderColor #6c5ce7
    FontColor #ffffff
}

actor       User                          #6c5ce7
participant "React Frontend"  as FE       #2d2d44
participant "FastAPI Backend"  as BE      #2d2d44
database    "Database\n(MySQL / SQLite)"  as DB #2d2d44
participant "LLM\n(Ollama Llama3)"        as LLM #2d2d44

== File Upload ==

User -> FE : Select / drop file (CSV, XLSX, etc.)
FE -> BE : POST /upload (multipart)
BE -> BE : Parse with Pandas + sanitize columns
BE -> DB : Create temp SQLite DB
BE -> LLM : Init SQL query chain
BE --> FE : { filename, rows, columns }
FE --> User : Show success badge

== Query ==

User -> FE : Type question + Enter
FE -> BE : POST /ask { question }
BE -> LLM : Generate SQL from question
LLM --> BE : Raw SQL
BE -> BE : Clean SQL (quotes, aliases, validate)
BE -> DB : Execute SELECT query
DB --> BE : Result rows
BE -> LLM : Summarize result → natural language
LLM --> BE : Friendly answer
BE --> FE : { query, answer, table_data }
FE -> FE : Render chart (auto-detect type)
FE --> User : Answer + Visualization + SQL

== Clear File ==

User -> FE : Click remove on file badge
FE -> BE : POST /clear-upload
BE -> BE : Delete temp SQLite, reset state
BE --> FE : OK
FE --> User : Reverted to default DB

@enduml
